<p>都处理好的金针菇请<br></p> 
<p>放在盆子里准备好，锅里热油<br></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//ae44/ae44c7452d84eeb931ed1e7ee81da7cf.com/large/191f000514823c686fc4"></p> 
<p>下锅<br></p> 
<p>八成油温的时候下锅炸</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//7e95/7e959a5afc8074933ae729882f96a926.com/large/191c0005281b3843e210"></p> 
<p>翻面<br></p> 
<p>一面炸至金黄再翻面<br></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//bdce/bdce4e9701f067bfdbea03bc2076d8ba.com/large/191c0005288d40d68731"></p> 
<p>出锅<br></p> 
<p>出锅，撒上调料（调料有胡椒粉，花椒粉，孜然粉，细盐）<br></p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//4c57/4c577a98a7c1d48fe0d63b969a2410e3.com/large/191c00052939b7289a2f"></p> 
